statement:
The purpose of EuroVoc is related to the delivery of multilingual public services. By establishing language equivalences between identical concepts expressed in different languages, it allows documents to be indexed in the language of the documentalist and searches to be made in the user’s language;

EuroVoc webpage:
https://op.europa.eu/en/web/eu-vocabularies/dataset/-/resource?uri=http://publications.europa.eu/resource/dataset/eurovoc
